name: ProfileObject
summary: Dictionary of parameter recieved after successful login.

properties.name: authorizationCode
properties.summary: A short-lived token used by your app for proof of authorization when interacting with the app's server counterpart.

properties.name: authorizedScopes
properties.summary: This value will contain a list of scopes for which the user provided authorization.

properties.name: identityToken
properties.summary: Web Token that securely communicates information about the user to your app.

properties.name: realUserStatus
properties.summary: Possible values for the real user indicator.

properties.name: state
properties.summary: A string that your app provided to the request that generated the credential.

properties.name: userId
properties.summary: An identifier associated with the authenticated user.
